Peggy Fears https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peggy_Fears 0 Peggy Fears (June 1, 1903 - August 24, 1994) was an American actress, who appeared in Broadway musical comedies during the 1920s and 1930s before becoming a Broadway producer.
